room_title: Escape room "C.S.I. - Mob Hit" by Escape Games at The River in Rancho Mirage
room_address: 71800 Hwy 111, Suite A-210 Rancho Mirage, CA 92270
room_description: You have been hired by the Benetti family to find out who was responsible for the nightclub murders inside the VIP Lounge. Corrupt officers on the force have helped place key evidence back at the scene and have distracted the investigators. This gives you a one hour window to identify the killers and get out before the police return.
